description: The new 4.8 and 4.7 magnitude tremors cause further damage after seven people died on Tuesday.
title: Croatia earthquake: Strong aftershocks hit after quake kills seven
title_page: Croatia earthquake: Strong aftershocks hit after quake kills seven - BBC News
maintext: A kindergarten also collapsed in Petrinja, but it was empty at the time of the quake. In a village just outside the town, a worker told the regional broadcaster N1 that nine of its 10 houses had been destroyed.
